**why —** They are the climb's locks made into a deck: a hand of five cards you must complete to keep ascending the tree.

**how —** Crystallized from Faxanadu (NES 1989) — Famicom Xanadu, on Falcom's licensed Xanadu name.

**◌ the mythos —** They are the climb's locks made into a deck: a hand of five cards you must complete to keep ascending the tree. a being of the World Tree and the climb to the Evil One

